casebody.data:
No. 09-9669. Shawn Gaines, Petitioner v. New York City Transit Authority, et al. 559 U.S. 1105, 130 S. Ct. 2428,

176 L. Ed. 2d 922,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3853. May 3, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until May 24, 2010, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
